  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A total balanced fluid replacement strategy is a promising concept for correcting
      hypovolemia. The effects of a balanced fluid management including a new balanced
      hydroxyethylstarch (HES) in elderly cardiac surgery patients will be studied.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
